reviewText: Great price for a great find. Was exactly as the seller stated. My first grade class LOVES these movies and it's great for me to be able to find these episodes at great prices for them.

My kids loved Bibleman when they were 5-8years old.  They are faith building shows that really grab kids attention.  My son watched this one just before he got his tonsils out.  It encouraged him to look to the Lord and not the circumstances.
It was the most coolest movie I have ever seen and it told god has not gave us a spirt of fear.  TED DUFFY,
